To close the vi editor press ESC + :q!

To write the text in the vi editor file, press i and then start typing the content

To Save and quit the vi editor : ESC + : wq

To see the content of file : cat <filename>

To see the current branch of Work : git branch

To add the remote in the git repo : git remote add <remote_name> <url>

To see the git remote of a repo : git remote -v

To change the remote Url : git remote add <prev_remote_name> <new_url>

To remove any remote from the git repo : git remote remove <remote_name>

To rename the remote name : git remote rename <old_remote> <new_remote>


